AppImage type-2 runtime
-----------------------

This project embeds the AppImage type-2 runtime binaries
(`src/os/linux/appimage/runtime-x86_64` and `runtime-aarch64`, upstream release
tag 20251108) **unmodified**, and concatenates one of them ahead of a SquashFS
image to produce a `build/<name>.AppImage` for a Linux `mfb build --app`. They
are redistributed exactly as the AppImage project publishes them.

The runtime is licensed under the MIT license, Copyright (c) 2004-23 probonopd.
Its full text — including the enumeration of the third-party code statically
linked into the runtime binary (musl libc, libfuse under LGPL-2.1, squashfuse
under BSD-2, libzstd, and zlib) — is shipped verbatim alongside the blobs at
`src/os/linux/appimage/LICENSE.type2-runtime`.

